            <p class="comment-content">喜欢刘震云这样说故事的路子。佩服他对现实的准确把握。看他的故事，总是既舒坦又难受，舒坦的是文字，难受的是他描写得太真实了。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="433680216">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-433680216" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-433680216" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="433680216">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bigfatwendy/">BigFatWendy</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2011-09-06</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">实在是太鸡毛</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

